18 E. Any person, firm or corporation claiming the exemption
19 herein provided for shall file each year for which exemption is
20 claimed, an application therefor with the county assessor of the
21 county in which the new, expanded or acquired facility is located.
22 The application shall be on a form or forms prescribed by the Tax
